  "time_ut": 1658739235,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba \u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dda \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There will be political stability under the leadership of the current president",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Justice, Prison Affairs and Constitutional Reform said that under the leadership of the current President Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, the establishment of political stability and the recovery of the economy in Sri Lanka will happen soon, and the 22nd Constitutional Amendment is being submitted to the Parliament for adoption. Lawyer Dr. Vijayadasa Rajapaksa said.",
        "The minister said this in a meeting between Thai Ambassador to Sri Lanka, Mr. Poj Hanpol, at the Ministry of Justice this morning.",
        "The Minister stated that he had the opportunity to deliver the keynote speech at the United Nations International Vesak Festival held in Thailand in 2016, and that Thailand made a great contribution when the event was held in Sri Lanka in 2017.",
        "The Minister of Justice gratefully recalled the contribution of Thailand to the economic and religious and cultural development of Sri Lanka at the present time for the re-establishment of Buddhism by returning the Buddhist Upasampa to Sri Lanka.",
        "The Ambassador said that it is hoped that the current problematic conditions in Sri Lanka will eventually lead to economic stability, and maximum diplomatic support will be provided for it."
      ],
